<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٥٨ -<span class="c5"> بَاب:</span> الدُّعَاءِ عَلَى الْمُشْرِكِينَ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">وَقَالَ ابْنُ مَسْعُودٍ:</span> قَالَ النَّبِيُّ <span class="special">ﷺ</span>: <span class="c2">(اللَّهُمَّ أَعِنِّي عَلَيْهِمْ بِسَبْعٍ كَسَبْعِ يُوسُفَ)</span>.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c4">[ر: ٩٦٢]</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">وَقَالَ:</span> <span class="c2">(اللَّهُمَّ عَلَيْكَ بِأَبِي جَهْلٍ)</span>.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
